tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE stock_analysis (
  symbol STRING,
  date DATE,
  strategy_id INT,
  buy_signal BOOLEAN,
  sell_signal BOOLEAN
);

CREATE TABLE stock_prices (
    stock_symbol VARCHAR PRIMARY KEY,
    date DATE PRIMARY KEY,
    open_price DECIMAL,
    high_price DECIMAL,
    low_price DECIMAL,
    close_price DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE strategy_analysis (
    analysis_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    stock_symbol VARCHAR,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    strategy_result VARCHAR
);

CREATE TABLE stock_prices (
    symbol TEXT,
    date DATE,
    open_price DECIMAL,
    close_price DECIMAL,
    volume INT
);

CREATE TABLE strategy_results (
    result_id UUID,
    strategy_id UUID,
    symbol TEXT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    ROI DECIMAL
);
